title: The Peter Schiff Show - 2011 Mar 11 FR [sebaygo1]
description:
.
							
The Peter Schiff Show
Friday, 11 March 2011


[sebaygo1]


Friday's guests are:

David Doniger, policy director & chief global warming lawyer at the Natural Resources Defense Council, on why Republican attempts at trimming the EPA's budget endangers humanity.

Michele Leber, chairwoman of the National Committee on Pay Equity, on America's bracing need for pay equity legislation to finally end the gender wage gap forever.

Dr. Scott Gottlieb, practicing physician & resident fellow at the American Enterprise Institute, on why Medicaid is worse than no coverage at all.


Andrew Schiff is guest-hosting for Peter.
